headline: 2 Reasons to Sell TPR and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Tapestry has been on fire lately. In the past six months alone, the company’s stock price has rocketed 56.7%, reaching $65.80 per share. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
